un me flegt zikh shpiln., keyn tsatskes azoy vi haynt iz nit geven azoy fil.

00:25:47.792 --> 00:25:53.588
flegt men zikh shpiln; me flegt, shpiln in BALL un me flegt loyfn un zikh bahaltn.

00:25:53.588 --> 00:25:58.845
me flegt, shpiln zikh mit zamd, mit shteyndlekh makhn azoy vi,

00:25:58.845 --> 00:26:02.031
 vi in a gesheft, me farkoyft.

00:26:02.031 --> 00:26:06.428
me f-, me flegt zikh, vinter flegt men zikh glitshn oyf shlitelekh, flegt men.

00:26:06.519 --> 00:26:12.674
 dos iz geven vos, oyfn hoyf, ⟨o-⟩ un s'iz geven, bayn ende hoyf iz geven azoy vi

00:26:12.674 --> 00:26:14.367
a gortn mit groz.

00:26:14.367 --> 00:26:20.571
flegt men, dortn, shpiln zikh oykhet, un me flegt lign, zikh opruen oyfn zun,

00:26:20.571 --> 00:26:26.103
a normale zakh, vi kinder. s'iz, dan iz geven a kind a kind, hot men ⟨oykh⟩ geshpilt vi kinder.

00:26:26.835 --> 00:26:27.639
ye.

00:26:30.514 --> 00:26:34.153
un, ale kinder fun farsheydene elter

00:26:34.383 --> 00:26:36.699
hobn ge- zikh geshpilt tsuzamen?

00:26:34.429 --> 00:26:46.944
ye, s'iz geven, eltere hobn zikh geshpilt mit eltere, yingere hobn zikh geshpilt mit yingere. yeder hot zikh gefunen zayne, zayne kinder, mit zayne fraynd, ye.

00:26:47.862 --> 00:26:48.902
un

00:26:49.414 --> 00:26:53.795
tate-mames hobn gelozt di kinder shpiln zikh a gantsn tog aleyn?

00:26:52.267 --> 00:26:53.898
s'- s'iz,

00:26:53.898 --> 00:26:56.596
s'iz dokh geven fray; m'hot nit moyre gehat.

00:26:56.822 --> 00:27:02.536
m'hot nit moyre gehat. tate-ma-, koydem iz men avek in der fri in SCHOOL, iz men dokh gekumen shoyn nokh mitik,

00:27:03.319 --> 00:27:08.191
un, di tate-mames zaynen dokh BUSY geven in gesheftn, ye.

00:27:08.191 --> 00:27:16.841
un oyfn hoyf iz dokh geven, keyner hot ⟨nit⟩ moyre gehat far keynem, un a shokhn oder vos hot gekukt, far ayenem kind azoy vi far an eygenem. m'iz ge-

00:27:16.841 --> 00:27:22.443
s'iz nit geven, m'hot nit tsugekhapt keyn kinder, m'hot nit derha-, s'iz nit geven azoyne zakhn a mol.

00:27:22.443 --> 00:27:24.322
ye. m'iz geven fray.

00:27:24.677 --> 00:27:25.606
⟨ye⟩.

00:27:26.269 --> 00:27:27.448
keyn,

00:27:27.448 --> 00:27:30.307
⟨⟩, keyn goyim zaynen a mol gekumen?

00:27:28.733 --> 00:27:32.180
 bloyz eyn goy hot bay undz gevoynt oyfn hoyf.

00:27:32.180 --> 00:27:36.121
er iz geven der JANITOR. der dozortse iz er geven,

00:27:36.121 --> 00:27:38.379
vos er flegt CLEANen di gasn.

00:27:38.487 --> 00:27:43.259
un, n- dos iz geven der eyntsike FAMILY, goyim.

00:27:43.259 --> 00:27:45.213
un azoy iz ale yidn geven.

00:27:45.425 --> 00:27:46.209
ye.

00:27:46.756 --> 00:27:53.522
tsi zaynen ale geven, studentn fun der zelber shule, tsi fun farsheydene...?

00:27:51.396 --> 00:27:54.883
NO, NO, NO. farshidene, farshidene.

00:27:54.574 --> 00:27:55.532
tsum bayshpil?

00:27:55.125 --> 00:27:57.532
andere zaynen gegangen in HEBREW,

00:27:57.606 --> 00:28:01.177
andere zaynen gegangen in poylishe, in povshekhnes,

00:28:01.369 --> 00:28:03.644
un a- alts in andere shuln.

00:28:03.644 --> 00:28:11.049
ikh bin gegangen vayter vayle mi- mayn shvester un mayn bruder zaynen gegangen f- frier, vu mir hobn gevoynt,

00:28:11.140 --> 00:28:16.123
zaynen zey gegangen in yene shul. bin ikh shoyn oykh gegangen. ober di andere zaynen gegangen arum

00:28:16.123 --> 00:28:18.511
Zavalner, nenter vi ikh, ye.

00:28:18.511 --> 00:28:20.989
ober farshidene SCHOO-, shules.

00:28:21.298 --> 00:28:22.670
s'iz geven poylish,

00:28:22.670 --> 00:28:24.802
HEBREW SCHOOLS, un yidishe.

00:28:24.974 --> 00:28:25.666
ye.

00:28:25.573 --> 00:28:28.110
un di andere zaynen geven frumer,

00:28:28.183 --> 00:28:30.095
tsi nit f- nit azoy frum?

00:28:29.753 --> 00:28:33.336
MOST zaynen rikhtik geven frume yidn,

00:28:33.336 --> 00:28:36.834
ober nit, ikh veys nit,

00:28:37.005 --> 00:28:42.769
vi frum bay yenem hot zikh gefirt in shtub. MOST zaynen geven frum, di mentshn, ye.

00:28:42.769 --> 00:28:45.921
efsher hot zikh gefunen eyn FAMILY, ober

00:28:45.921 --> 00:28:47.740
m'hot nit gevust rikhtik.

00:28:48.096 --> 00:28:51.465
m'iz nit geforn shabes, m'hot nit ge⟨ton⟩ shabes.

00:28:51.488 --> 00:28:54.184
es iz geven a yidisher lebn, ye.

00:28:54.184 --> 00:28:55.676
a frumer lebn.

00:28:55.676 --> 00:28:56.354
ye.

00:28:57.006 --> 00:29:00.476
hot men, diskutirt vegn khasidizm

00:29:00.617 --> 00:29:01.488
demolt?

00:29:01.444 --> 00:29:13.014
 ken zayn, di eltern, ober, mir hot dos, ikh, hob nit geredt. ober di eltern b- iz azoy vi ⟨in,⟩ mentshn, hobn farsheydene yedies un me redt farsheydene zakhn.

00:29:13.324 --> 00:29:14.096
ye.

00:29:14.117 --> 00:29:17.219
OKAY, itster vet men iberbaytn di tashme.
